[SR][NORM]

350
00:23:08,900 --> 00:23:11,680
You can change one card into any other card.

351
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:12,790
Gon, quick!

352
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:15,180
Transform on! Gold Dust Girl.

353
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:16,290
Gold Dust Girl
A girl who releases golden dust.
One bath a day will net 500G.
Very shy and quiet.

354
00:23:15,950 --> 00:23:16,710
Gain.

