00:23:17,710 --> 00:23:18,870
G.I. Tutorial

356
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:21,250
Continue!

357
00:23:26,570 --> 00:23:29,430
Next time: Ging's Friends x And x True Friends.

358
00:23:29,430 --> 00:23:31,580
Think I can make a hundred friends?

359
00:23:31,580 --> 00:23:32,470
You'll be fine.

360
